title: Must Read: Jane Birkin's Original Birkin Bag Goes to Auction, Rent the Runway Projects Double-Digit Subscriber Growth
description: These are the stories making headlines in fashion on Friday. The original Birkin bag — the prototype made for actress Jane Birkin — is going up for auction as part of the Sotheby's Paris Fashion Icons sale on July 10. There is no public estimate for how high the bidding ...Continue reading
author: Catie Pusateri
